I/CanvasRenderingContext2D/getTransform\"><code>getTransform()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/isPointInPath\"><code>isPointInPath()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/isPointInStroke\"><code>isPointInStroke()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/lineTo\"><code>lineTo()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/measureText\"><code>measureText()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/moveTo\"><code>moveTo()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/putImageData\"><code>putImageData()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/quadraticCurveTo\"><code>quadraticCurveTo()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/rect\"><code>rect()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/resetTransform\"><code>resetTransform()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/restore\"><code>restore()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/rotate\"><code>rotate()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/save\"><code>save()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/scale\"><code>scale()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/scrollPathIntoView\"><code>scrollPathIntoView()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/setLineDash\"><code>setLineDash()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/setTransform\"><code>setTransform()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/stroke\"><code>stroke()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/strokeRect\"><code>strokeRect()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/strokeText\"><code>strokeText()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/transform\"><code>transform()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/translate\"><code>translate()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p>Die&nbsp;<code><strong>CanvasRenderingContext2D</strong></code><strong><code>.textAlign</code></strong>&nbsp;Eigenschaft&nbsp;der Canvas 2D API spezifiert die aktuelle Textausrichtung welche beim zeichnen von Text verwendet wird.</p>\n\n<p>Nehmen Sie in Acht, dass die Ausrichtung auf dem x Wert der <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/fillText\"><code>fillText()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> Methode basiert. Wenn&nbsp;<code>textAlign</code> &nbsp;<code>\"center\"</code>&nbsp;ist,&nbsp; dann würde der Text an der Stelle&nbsp;<code>x - (width / 2)</code>&nbsp;gezeichnet werden.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><var><em>ctx</em>.textAlign = \"left\" || \"right\" || \"center\" || \"start\" || \"end\";</var>\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"optionen","title":"Optionen","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Mögliche Werte:</p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"left\"><code>left</code></dt>\n <dd>Der Text wird linksbündig ausgerichtet.</dd>\n <dt id=\"right\"><code>right</code></dt>\n <dd>Der Text wird rechtsbündig ausgerichtet.</dd>\n <dt id=\"center\"><code>center</code></dt>\n <dd>Der Text wird zentiert ausgerichtet.</dd>\n <dt id=\"start\"><code>start</code></dt>\n <dd>Der Text wird am normalen Start der Zeile ausgerichtet. (Links -oder rechtsbündig, je nach Sprache).</dd>\n <dt id=\"end\"><code>end</code></dt>\n <dd>Der Text wird am normalen Ende der Zeile&nbsp;ausgerichtet (Links -oder rechtsbündig, je nach Sprache).</dd>\n</dl>\n\n<p>Der Standardwert ist&nbsp;<code>start</code>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"beispiele","title":"Beispiele","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"using_the_textalign_property","title":"Benutzung der&nbsp;<code>textAlign</code> Eigenschaft","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Ein einfaches Beispiel welches die <code>textAlign</code>&nbsp;Eigenschaft benutzt um die Textausrichtung zu ändern.</p>\n\n<h4 id=\"html\">HTML</h4>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>canvas</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>canvas<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>canvas</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<h4 id=\"javascript\">JavaScript</h4>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> canvas <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'canvas'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> ctx <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> canvas<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getContext</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'2d'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nctx<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>font <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'48px serif'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nctx<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>textAlign <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'left'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nctx<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">strokeText</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'Hello world'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">100</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<p>Ändern Sie den Code um Ihre Änderungen im Canvas zu sehen:</p>\n\n\n\n<p><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"Playable code sample\" id=\"frame_playable_code\" width=\"700\" height=\"360\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/de/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/textAlign/_sample_.playable_code.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></p>","titleAsText":"Benutzung der textAlign Eigenschaft"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"spezifikationen","title":"Spezifikationen","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/scripting.html#dom-context-2d-textalign\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von 'CanvasRenderingContext2D.textAlign' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Lebender Standard</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browserkompatibilität","id":"browserkompatibilität","isH3":false,"query":"api.CanvasRenderingContext2D.textAlign","dataURL":"/de/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/textAlign/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"siehe_auch","title":"Siehe auch","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li>Das Interface&nbsp;welches es definiert,&nbsp;<a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D\"><code>CanvasRenderingContext2D</code></a>.</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Syntax","id":"syntax"},{"text":"Beispiele","id":"beispiele"},{"text":"Spezifikationen","id":"spezifikationen"},{"text":"Browserkompatibilität","id":"browserkompatibilität"},{"text":"Siehe auch","id":"siehe_auch"}],"summary":"Die CanvasRenderingContext2D.textAlign Eigenschaft der Canvas 2D API spezifiert die aktuelle Textausrichtung welche beim zeichnen von Text verwendet wird.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"CanvasRenderingContext2D.textAlign","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"CanvasRenderingContext2D.textAlign","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"CanvasRenderingContext2D.textAlign","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"CanvasRenderingContext2D.textAlign","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"CanvasRenderingContext2D.textAlign","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"de/web/api/canvasrenderingcontext2d/textalign","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/de/web/api/canvasrenderingcontext2d/textalign/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/de/docs/Web","title":"Webtechnologien für Entwickler"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API Referenz"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D","title":"CanvasRenderingContext2D"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/textAlign","title":"CanvasRenderingContext2D.textAlign"}],"pageTitle":"CanvasRenderingContext2D.textAlign - Web API Referenz | MDN","noIndexing":false}}